Scope of this repository and what it does NOT contain
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This repository is a READ-ONLY connector (interface layer). It deliberately
contains only:

  - connector/tool code (Apache-2.0)
  - JSON Schemas describing the shape of what a caller RECEIVES (Apache-2.0)
  - documentation (CC BY 4.0 unless a file states otherwise)
  - small SAMPLE manifests (a handful of records per corpus, for demonstration)
  - pointers to the canonical corpus repositories and datasets

It does NOT contain, and is not intended to distribute:

  - the full legal corpora (see the canonical repositories / datasets)
  - any corpus-construction, ingestion, verification or provenance-building
    methodology, tooling, or schemas
  - embeddings, premium metadata, cross-reference graphs, monitoring logic,
    scoring models, hosted-search indexes, or API credentials

